{"type":"message","id":"546fa9c6","parentId":"97ac0959","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:21:34.359Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tbwbgdck01zg_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 3516\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='research/CFI_COMPRESSION_EXPERIMENT.md' new_len=1537\n[mutation proposed] research/CFI_COMPRESSION_EXPERIMENT.md\n[master eb96a55] pulse: 2026-03-24 122115\n 6 files changed, 231 insertions(+), 139 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 122115.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 122115.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 122016.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 122115 - The CFI analysis revealed that 44.8% of invariants are noise (CFI=0) and only 5.7% are true causal anchors (CFI>=0.7). The pending action is to run a CFI-weighted compression experiment comparing prediction quality against the frequency baseline.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"tide-breeze","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 3516\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='research/CFI_COMPRESSION_EXPERIMENT.md' new_len=1537\n[mutation proposed] research/CFI_COMPRESSION_EXPERIMENT.md\n[master eb96a55] pulse: 2026-03-24 122115\n 6 files changed, 231 insertions(+), 139 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 122115.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 122115.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 122016.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 122115 - The CFI analysis revealed that 44.8% of invariants are noise (CFI=0) and only 5.7% are true causal anchors (CFI>=0.7). The pending action is to run a CFI-weighted compression experiment comparing prediction quality against the frequency baseline.\n","name":"powershell C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"tim